      </p>

      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Discord user IDs, server IDs, and channel IDs</li>
        <li>Message content only when required to process commands</li>
        <li>Basic usage statistics (command usage, interactions)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How We Use Data</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>To provide and operate bot features</li>
        <li>To improve stability and performance</li>
        <li>To respond to commands and interactions</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Data Storage</h2>
      <p>
        Data is stored only as long as necessary. We do not sell, rent,
        or share user data with third parties.
      </p>

      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>
        The Bot uses Discord APIs and may use third-party services.
        These services follow their own privacy policies.
      </p>

      <h2>User Rights</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>You may stop data collection by removing the bot from your server</li>
        <li>You may contact the bot owner with questions or concerns</li>
      </ul>

